{"tid":1438633,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"關於近期台灣手搖飲品店事件，有少少野想講下","createTime":"2019-08-09T22:27:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T12:48:04.000Z","uid":165430,"like":19,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"307d440925abe47408df4283905b8a4abd96db3e","tid":1438633,"uid":165430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T22:27:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">希望大家唔好上一頁住，比小小時間睇一睇我想講既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n關於所謂<span style=\"font-size: large;\">貢茶</span>嘅微博，並冇官方認證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n我本身冇用微博，但今次事件同一芳同Coco個單性質差唔多，所以專登上去睇下呢個所謂既專頁<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Tj12J3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Tj12J3.png&h=4dbf3a22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家都知道fact check嘅重要性，既然台灣及香港代理方面從未發出過聲明，無理由完全相信呢個專頁所講嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且，貢茶官網仍然係將香港，台灣歸類為亞洲，並唔係中國，可見貢茶並無意將兩地歸為類中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wqsvbFj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwqsvbFj.png&h=bc11d945&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就近期一芳、Coco、貢茶等事件，呢啲加盟店都被中國代理公司一同歸類，由其一芳香港代理公司都發出聲明大陸微博所講嘅言論係無關係，其實係對台灣及香港嘅代理公司甚至對呢啲店鋪係極不公平<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而亦都好明顯望到中国方面想打壓呢啲台灣手搖飲品，目的大概係想分化大眾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />令我地產生台灣手搖飲品=大陸野。<br />\n如果你真係相信大陸微博所講既聲明，證明你已經成功中左中国既計。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申返：貢茶員工，全店都支持反送中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">時代革命</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">沒有暴徒</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">只有暴政</span></span>"},{"pid":"53db2feb2876bfc7478c1660fa4b73be1c93ca4e","tid":1438633,"uid":109670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T22:29:50.000Z","msg":"同意佢地係想分化<br />\n同埋有去過大陸都見過成街都假貢榮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"398a6a89a6a6441ce96fdba5488d6254e18c92ab","tid":1438633,"uid":165430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"53db2feb2876bfc7478c1660fa4b73be1c93ca4e","tid":1438633,"uid":109670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T22:29:50.000Z","msg":"同意佢地係想分化<br />\n同埋有去過大陸都見過成街都假貢榮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T22:32:53.000Z","msg":"跟本呢啲加盟店就係每個地區有唔同做法<br />\n人地大陸鳩up一下，成班人就即刻割席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />分化就係咁簡單"},{"pid":"23c5702c0f3775212a1d5061faa9b07733fd6fd3","tid":1438633,"uid":288849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T00:31:07.000Z","msg":"文宣商戰：撐「五大訴求、缺一不可」良心認證標誌店舖消費推廣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1438675\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1438675</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4a4662503b9bf6c1d7456fbb3946802267163a71","tid":1438633,"uid":7306,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:10:19.000Z","msg":"喂<br />\n喂喂<br />\n<br />\n收皮啦<br />\n<br />\n你係公司大佬<br />\n分公司亂up24你唔識收返經營權？"},{"pid":"f37e877ba8306cf3ca2dbee50b7f933806529d39","tid":1438633,"uid":274136,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:31:53.000Z","msg":"<strong><em><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不撤不散 各自努力<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></span></ins></em></strong><br />\n唔好意思 阻你一陣<br />\n-<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港人重點日程：<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>8月9-11日</strong>：機場和你飛&bull;萬人接機&bull;一連三日(1300)</span><br />\n-<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>8月10日</strong>：銀髮族遞信「900警總」&gt;「1000律政司辦公室」&gt;「1100特首辦」<br />\n<strong>8月10日</strong>：守護孩子未來親子遊行（1030愛丁堡廣場）<br />\n<strong>8月10日</strong>：大埔遊行（1400大埔巴士總站）（反對通知書）</span><br />\n-<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>8月11日</strong>：港島東遊行（1300維多利亞公園）<br />\n<strong>8月11日</strong>：深水埗遊行（1430楓樹街遊樂場）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">逢星期五，日擺買！減少家庭支出</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"e33f6f205b71cc767cdff25382faccb467952922","tid":1438633,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:32:15.000Z","msg":"None of my business... 唔好搵香港人錢 人民幣香"},{"pid":"3a35f474f1c4de6afad75277d6f4c208cca25d1a","tid":1438633,"uid":176449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a4662503b9bf6c1d7456fbb3946802267163a71","tid":1438633,"uid":7306,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:10:19.000Z","msg":"喂<br />\n喂喂<br />\n<br />\n收皮啦<br />\n<br />\n你係公司大佬<br />\n分公司亂up24你唔識收返經營權？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:25:48.000Z","msg":"係 嗰間茶理史都收咗皮"},{"pid":"4fc559b2cf84b3569838cbbe3ded088a1462a7cd","tid":1438633,"uid":176834,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T07:58:16.000Z","msg":"貢茶係難飲到無論親唔親共都冇人想飲"},{"pid":"1998b7c3b21991fd72ad9795aea20e16edaea873","tid":1438633,"uid":157508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:28:57.000Z","msg":"嗱樓主如果真如你所講個微博唔係經認證，即並非正式由台灣嘅貢茶發出<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咁點解台灣嘅貢茶唔出嚟否認？</span><br />\n你成間鋪嘅人反送中，多謝<br />\n但間公司呢？"},{"pid":"346d9c8a7d5ec6aea5576353a